      "options": ["Ontem comi pizza", "Quando era criança, comia pizza sempre", "Comi a pizza toda", "Vou comer pizza"],
      "correct_index": 1,
      "explanation": "The imperfect tense 'comia' describes habitual actions in the past."
    },
    {
      "type": "matching_pairs",
      "prompt": "Match with pretérito perfeito",
      "pairs": [
        ["To speak - I spoke", "Falar - Falei"],
